about.summary: An iterative algorithm for solving a convex formulation of the biclustering problem.

name: r-cvxbiclustr
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.0.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-cvxbiclustr
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/cvxbiclustr_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/cvxbiclustr/cvxbiclustr_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ae1d5b5a425705aafdd5ac90dfe773534a8a7e89a808089e2b0d9b8dfc2f6702

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1001
  skip: true  # [win32]
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{posix}}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{posix}}make
    - {{posix}}sed  # [win]
    - {{posix}}coreutils  # [win]
    - {{posix}}sed               # [win]
    - {{posix}}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-matrix
    - r-igraph
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{native}}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-matrix
    - r-igraph

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('cvxbiclustr')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('cvxbiclustr')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=cvxbiclustr
  license: MIT
  summary: An iterative algorithm for solving a convex formulation of the biclustering problem.
  license_family: MIT

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
    - cbrueffer
    - dbast
    - PertuyF
